    "author_association": "COLLABORATOR",
    "body": "Blindly speaking \"I’ll do this thing\" is bad. Best design for \"WhatIf\" is to communicate as much useful information to the user as possible in order to prevent irreversible erroneous changes.",
    "created_at": "2021-01-18T06:32:55Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/PowerShell/PowerShell/issues/13620#issuecomment-762017204",
    "id": 762017204,
